<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #f59e0b; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .body { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; }
    .detail { margin: 8px 0; }
    .label { font-weight: bold; color: #6b7280; }
    .reason { background: #fffbeb; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; margin: 12px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Chargeback Notification</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
      <p>A chargeback has been filed for a transaction on your account.</p>
      <div class="detail"><span class="label">Dispute ID:</span> {{disputeId}}</div>
      <div class="detail"><span class="label">Transaction ID:</span> {{transactionId}}</div>
      <div class="detail"><span class="label">Amount:</span> {{currency}} {{amount}}</div>
      <div class="detail"><span class="label">Merchant:</span> {{merchantName}}</div>
      <div class="detail"><span class="label">Date Filed:</span> {{date}}</div>
      <div class="reason"><strong>Reason:</strong> {{chargebackReason}}</div>
      <p>We are reviewing this dispute and will provide updates as more information becomes available.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>PayFlow Notification Service</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
